'''內灣中心站'''（{{lang-en|Inlet Centre Station}}）是[[加拿大|加拿大]][[卑詩省|卑詩省]][[大溫哥華地區|大溫哥華地區]][[滿地寶|滿地寶]]一座[[溫哥華架空列車|架空列車]][[千禧線|千禧線]]車站。此站位於滿地寶市班納公路（{{lang|en|Barnet Highway}}）與艾奧高路（{{lang|en|Ioco Road}}）的交界處，為[[運輸聯線|運輸聯線]]收費架構中三號收費區的其中一個車站。

此站在原計劃中稱為艾奧高站（{{lang|en|Ioco Station}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.evergreenline.gov.bc.ca/documents/Postcards/120817_ELRT_GeneralInfo_Postcard_FINAL.pdf|title=Evergreen Line General Information Postcard|publisher=British Columbia Ministry of Transportation|accessdate=2013-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130320035608/http://www.evergreenline.gov.bc.ca/documents/Postcards/120817_ELRT_GeneralInfo_Postcard_FINAL.pdf|archive-date=2013-03-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，2013年3月則改為現稱<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mingpaovan.com/htm/news/20130324/vap1h.htm|title=長青線敲定7站名 造價14.3億 連接本滿高3市|publisher=《明報》加西版|date=2013-03-24|accessdate=2013-03-24|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130427032659/http://www.mingpaovan.com/htm/news/20130324/vap1h.htm|archivedate=2013-04-27}}</ref>。此站工程於2013年6月展開<ref>{{cite web|url=http://egrtconstruction.ca/construction-traffic-updates/port-moody/|title=EGRT Construction: Port Moody|publisher=EGRT Construction|accessdate=2013-06-14|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130703063839/http://egrtconstruction.ca/construction-traffic-updates/port-moody/|archivedate=2013-07-03}}</ref>，並於2016年12月2日聯同千禧線的[[長青延線|長青延線]]一起開幕<ref name="open-date">{{cite news|last1=Brown|first1=Scott|title=TransLink will open Evergreen Line on Dec. 2|date=2016-11-07|accessdate=2016-11-07|work=Vancouver Sun|url=http://vancouversun.com/news/local-news/translink-will-open-evergreen-line-on-dec-2|archive-date=2016-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107222150/http://vancouversun.com/news/local-news/translink-will-open-evergreen-line-on-dec-2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://bc.ctvnews.ca/tri-cities-rejoice-the-long-awaited-evergreen-line-opens-1.3186748|title=Tri-Cities rejoice: The long-awaited Evergreen Line opens|publisher=CTV Vancouver|date=2016-12-02|accessdate=2016-12-02|archive-date=2016-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161203153512/http://bc.ctvnews.ca/tri-cities-rejoice-the-long-awaited-evergreen-line-opens-1.3186748|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

